## ============================================================
## 1. EXPERIAN OAUTH2 TOKEN (WORKING)
## ============================================================

Endpoint: POST https://uat-in-api.experian.com/oauth2/v1/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Status: WORKING

Request body (form-urlencoded):
  grant_type=password
  client_id=${EXPERIAN_CLIENT_ID}
  client_secret=${EXPERIAN_CLIENT_SECRET}
  username=${EXPERIAN_USERNAME}
  password=${EXPERIAN_PASSWORD}

Response: { access_token: "...", expires_in: 1800 }

Implementation: paisawalla/backend/src/services/experianTokenService.js
  - Caches token for 28 minutes (1680s) out of 30-min expiry
  - Auto-refreshes on expiry
  - Deduplicates concurrent token requests
  - Invalidates on 401 response from any API call

Working curl:
  curl -X POST "https://uat-in-api.experian.com/oauth2/v1/token" \
    -H "Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded" \
    -d "grant_type=password&client_id=${EXPERIAN_CLIENT_ID}&client_secret=${EXPERIAN_CLIENT_SECRET}&username=${EXPERIAN_USERNAME}&password=${EXPERIAN_PASSWORD}"


