### 2a. Registration / Enhanced Match (WORKING)

Endpoint: POST https://uat-in-api.experian.com/ecs/ecv-api/v1/enhanced-match
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer ${token}
Status: WORKING

IMPORTANT URL NOTES:
  - CORRECT endpoint: /ecs/ecv-api/v1/enhanced-match
  - WRONG (tried first): /ecs/ecv-api/v1/register-enhanced-match-mobile-otp (returned "Validation with Experian Failed")
  - WRONG (tried second): /ecs/ecv-api/v1/register-enhanced-matchmobile-otp (returned HTTP 500)
  - The working URL was found from the user's Postman collection

Request params (form-urlencoded):
  clientName=UNIMOBILE_EM          (from env: EXPERIAN_CLIENT_NAME)
  allowInput=1
  allowEdit=1
  allowCaptcha=1
  allowConsent=1
  allowEmailVerify=1
  allowVoucher=1
  voucherCode=TestOWW8H            (from env: EXPERIAN_VOUCHER_CODE)
  firstName=Adrian
  surName=Fernandes
  mobileNo=9769051199
  email=adrian.fernandes@theunimobile.com
  reason=Find out my credit score
  noValidationByPass=0
  emailConditionalByPass=1
  pan=SCXPF1234J                   (NOTE: ends with J, not I)

Response fields (IMPORTANT - has trailing underscores):
  {
    "errorString": null,
    "stageOneId_": "5096048",      <-- NOT "stgOneHitId"
    "stageTwoId_": "4346655",      <-- NOT "stgTwoHitId"
    "showHtmlReportForCreditReport": ...,
    "newUserId": 1857728,
    "subscriptionMsg": null
  }

Implementation: paisawalla/backend/src/services/experianEcvService.js (register method)
  - Maps stageOneId_ -> stgOneHitId, stageTwoId_ -> stgTwoHitId internally
  - Also captures newUserId

Working curl:
  curl -X POST 'https://uat-in-api.experian.com/ecs/ecv-api/v1/enhanced-match' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded' \
    -H 'Authorization: Bearer ${TOKEN}' \
    --data-urlencode 'clientName=UNIMOBILE_EM' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowInput=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowEdit=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowCaptcha=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowConsent=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowEmailVerify=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'allowVoucher=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'voucherCode=TestOWW8H' \
    --data-urlencode 'firstName=Adrian' \
    --data-urlencode 'surName=Fernandes' \
    --data-urlencode 'mobileNo=9769051199' \
    --data-urlencode 'email=adrian.fernandes@theunimobile.com' \
    --data-urlencode 'reason=Find out my credit score' \
    --data-urlencode 'noValidationByPass=0' \
    --data-urlencode 'emailConditionalByPass=1' \
    --data-urlencode 'pan=SCXPF1234J' \
    --data-urlencode '='


